{
  "stem": "24884.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I got pregnant, it was no time to be pregnant.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we tried to eliminate my pregnancy, which somehow didn't work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we took a family doctor-- the family doctor off my husband's family into-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we-- we talked to him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was very, very anti-Nazi always.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a Dr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Koenig.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he examined me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he said he would come to the house and he would help me deliver the baby.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] As it turned out, about a few months, three months or so before-- I don't know exactly how long before.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He said to me it will not be possible. , The baby's not lying in a perfect position.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And will be all kinds-- and I have to try to go into a hospital.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was a route I  remember to go to Yugoslavia to one of the other countries.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they wanted to get me out of Germany for the duration of the birth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- but-- also that didn't work out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my husband had the bright idea to talk to a friend of his, who was also like him, a Mischling, and try to get his sister to give me her papers that I could go under her name to a hospital because she was legal.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was married to another Mischling, and they lived legal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as  he talked to him, it turned out that he said, no.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It can't be done.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because his sister just had a baby.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she can't have three months later another one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this friend of his-- his name was Hans-- had a girlfriend, very nice girl, who was also very, very anti-Nazi.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
